   NETHAWAY-COLUMN _ WACO, Texas _ If Clinton really is deeply
disturbed about nationwide reports of police violence and civil
rights abuses, he should show some leadership by ordering Attorney
General Janet Reno to conduct a full-scale investigation. (Rowland
Nethaway is senior editor of the Waco Tribune-Herald) MOVED
