<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 
 This ``separate buy'' article is from Latin Trade magazine,
America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    REVENGE OF THE NERDS. Mexico's Miguel de Icaza and his ragtag
army take on Microsoft's stranglehold on PC software.
 &HT;    Filed as BC-MEXICAN-COMPUTER-WHIZ-LATINTRADE-NYTSF.
 &HT;    
 (To publish this article, it must be purchased _ the rate is not
