<HEADLINE>
RACETRACK ON THE BAY SEEKS TO REVIVE ITS FORTUNE 
</HEADLINE>
   (EDs: Filed on the ``f,'' financial, and ``s,'' sports, wires)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By GEORGE RAINE  
 c.1999 San Francisco Examiner  
<TEXT>
