<P>
   UNDATED _ I'd feel a whole lot better about airstrikes over
Yugoslavia if the United States and the North Atlantic Treaty
Organization had some kind of plan for what happens if, heaven
forbid, the Butcher of Belgrade doesn't back down. By J.R. LABBE.
