WING-COMMANDER (Los Angeles) _ Chris Roberts says his $25 million
debut feature ``Wing Commander'' wasn't that big of a leap from
games. By David Bloom. 
 
 
PLEASANTVILLE-DVD (Los Angeles) _ ``Pleasantville'' on DVD is maybe
the best way to see what director Gary Ross and his team had in
mind. By David Bloom. 
 
 
HEDDA-REVIEW (Los Angeles) _ Review of ``Hedda Gabler'' with
Annette Bening. By Reed Johnson. 

