<P>
   Here are the stories New York Times editors are planning for
Page 1, Saturday, March 27. The N.Y. Times News Service Night
Supervisor is Lynn Hoogenboom; phone: (888) 346-9867; e-mail:
lyhoog(at)nytimes.com.
