   HOUSE ATTENDANCE Present and Voting
</P>
<P>
   ------------------
</P>
<P>
   THERE ARE NO NEW SENATE BILLS:
</P>
<P>
   THERE ARE NO NEW HOUSE BILLS:
</P>
