<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; FOR SUNDAY, MARCH 28 &LR;
</P>
<P>
   ELIMINATE: INVEST-WINE.
</P>
<P>
   The New York Times News Service will send the following Money
and Business articles for release Sunday, March 28, 1999:
</P>
<P>
   &UR; ON THE SECTION FRONT &LR;
</P>
